author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Wood stud anchoring tips in concrete block…this is not an exterior wall, so I’m using regular wood. I pre-drill the studs and use a Makita hammer drill for the concrete block. I make the hole 1/4 inch longer than the Tapcons. Then I use an impact driver to fasten screws. Many thanks to @makitatools for sending some of the tools for this project 🔥#carpentry #concreteblocks #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
title: Wood Stud Anchoring Tips in Concrete Block - #shorts #carpentry #homerepairtutor
